{"tid":1441891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記住四個字：「常在戰場」","createTime":"2019-08-10T18:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:40:59.000Z","uid":240871,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"35864b676bbb22d10f03b7a9711489a34e6c9ec9","tid":1441891,"uid":240871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:33:26.000Z","msg":"我係其中一個今日7點零喺經過大圍嘅火車入面硬食催淚彈嘅人<br />\n<br />\n自己叫好彩有個普通手術口罩跟身，雖然都係擋唔到煙，但叫做好過冇。見到全車9成人連口罩都冇個，全部奶晒嘢<br />\n大家純粹係搭緊火車出九龍行街食飯，乜gear都冇，喺最冇防備嘅情況下食彈，仲要唔少係細路同老人家，除咗慘之外都唔知可以點形容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但我一啲都唔覺得自己係無辜被波及，或者今次係無妄之災<br />\n<br />\n根本而家已經係全香港人同香港政府嘅total war，只要喺香港境內，就要有心理準備隨時比敵人搞<br />\n<br />\n全香港十八區每一區都可以隨時變成戰場</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我都明冇可能隨便落個街都帶 / 上齊gear，但我覺得第一步係<strong><ins>每個香港人都起碼做好隨時食催淚彈嘅心理準備</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">雖然唔係有效應付到啲彈，但大家都最少要隨身帶備三樣嘢：<br />\n1. 口罩<br />\n2. 清水<br />\n3. 紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n喺你完全冇準備下食彈嘅情況下，呢三樣嘢起碼幫到你些少。當然，呢啲只係最最最最最低要求，連gear都算不上<br />\n如果做到嘅話，隨身越多gear越好，詳情請睇香城online攻略：<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4/edit#gid=187459515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4%2Fedit%23gid%3D187459515&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=4c499a24\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16jsUWJDS0YTIlICECOfDtzKt4XIgJVuzER0c0I4wFQ4/edit#gid=187459515</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但最重要，其實係個心態：<ins>要明白全個香港已經等同戰場，同政府戰爭就係日常</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n所以忽然食催淚彈並唔係好出奇嘅事，食咗嘅話唔好慌亂，有能力就幫下身邊嘅人<br />\n<br />\n呢個已經唔係抗唔抗爭，係唔係示威者嘅問題，只要你活喺香港，就係活喺一個戰場，就應該要有隨時提防敵襲嘅心理狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b30fcfeb4ea65e0c81defecde87bdb64a7162e","tid":1441891,"uid":251001,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKJm9B6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKJm9B6.jpg&h=62cfb11f&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>出沒注意</strong>⚠️<strong>時刻保持警覺 獨立思考！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>凡事抱有懷疑態度！不輕信他人！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"0c9dd28c668d9d176a49a8b775f3c2d589a4d94c","tid":1441891,"uid":240871,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53b30fcfeb4ea65e0c81defecde87bdb64a7162e","tid":1441891,"uid":251001,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKJm9B6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKJm9B6.jpg&h=62cfb11f&s={SIZE}\" /><strong>出沒注意</strong>⚠️<strong>時刻保持警覺 獨立思考！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>凡事抱有懷疑態度！不輕信他人！</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:35:46.000Z","msg":"P唔P都要自己用腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45d9cfe71cebe880ec1069e3deef308291db9e6","tid":1441891,"uid":251001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s